<div class="container STATE one-edge-shadow profile-form">
  <h2 class="greeting">FlipCoin is Live in Presale!</h2>
  <p class="paragraph center announcement">
 	 	CoinFlip & the FlipCoin team are extremely excited to announce  deployment of our token and crowdsale.<br><br>
 	 	Thank you to everyone for your continued support!<br>
 	 	<span class="bold">Scroll down to get started!</span>
  </p>
  <p class="pp-description" style="margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-top: 35px !important;">
  	<i class="fa fa-heart fa-2x"></i>
